<D>__{yes. it's great. and you got the scholarship! congratulations, honey.}
<C>__{toby}
<D>__{yeah, i'm out! i'm outta here! maybe i will crash and burn, but it's a chance, so i'm gone! i'm history, histoire. nobody's gonna tell me what to do now, nobody. i'm free as a bird. sayonara nest.}
<P>__{(yells it; really bawls it out)}
<D>__{heaven on a june day!}
<A>__{caroline's smile becomes fixed during toby's speech and she begins to regard him oddly.}
<C>__{caroline}
<P>__{(weakly)}
<D>__{yeah, heaven on a june day...}
<C>__{toby}
<D>__{what'd he say about you having a job in d.c.?}
